text: Shanna Lynn (born March 28, 1975) is an American model, actress, and former beauty queen. She won Miss New York USA in 1995. She became Miss USA when Chelsi Smith won Miss Universe. Moakler was the Playmate of the Month for Playboy in December 2001. Moakler was born in Providence, Rhode Island. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Rhode Island Category:American models Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Beauty pageant winners
